reviewText:
Well, is George Kollias, just AMAZING!
Lots of great workouts, plenty of material to work with!
Recommended!

I purchased this as a gift for someone who plays drums.  it was reasonably priced and what he selected.  I later asked him how he liked it and he said it was "pretty cool".  That would mean something to someone into drumming but personally I haven't a clue.  Sorry I cannot comment further.  :)
great tutorial, it's very long, George is really good at teaching and the footage is very professional, happy to have it.
